'''史丹福大厦'''（{{lang-en|'''Stamford House'''}}，原名：'''Oranje Building'''）位於[[新加坡|新加坡]]市中心、[[史丹福路|史丹福路]]與[[禧街|禧街]]的交界處，現為[[購物中心|購物中心]]，是一棟建於1904年的歷史建築物。曾一度被用作酒店用途<ref name="Warren Fernandez">{{cite news | author = Warren Fernandez| title = Eight ideas to make this a livelier city | publisher = ''[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]]'' | date = 26 August 2006| page=}}</ref>，[[新加坡日佔時期|新加坡日佔時期]]被[[皇軍|皇軍]]霸佔。1963年易手，並改名為史丹福大厦。

物業於1991至94年間進行了耗資1千3百萬星幣的修復工程<ref name="Ida Bachtiar">{{cite news | author = Ida Bachtiar| title = Stamford House $13 million later | publisher = ''[[The_Sunday_Times_(Singapore)|The Sunday Times]]'' | date = 22 May 1994| page=SP4}}</ref>，至1995年重新開放，並重現了原本[[威尼斯|威尼斯]]式[[文藝復興建築|文藝復興建築]]的風采。<ref name="Stephanie Yeo May 1994">{{cite news | author = Stephanie Yeo| title = Cosiness is part of plan | publisher = ''[[The_Sunday_Times_(Singapore)|The Sunday Times]]'' | date = 22 May 1994| page=SP4}}</ref><ref name="Stephanie Yeo Nov 1994">{{cite news | author = Stephanie Yeo| title = Stamford House latest centre in furnishings | publisher = ''[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]]'' | date = 24 November 1994| page=L4}}</ref><ref name="Stephanie Yeo Mar 1995">{{cite news | author = Stephanie Yeo| title = Stamford House enters growing $2 billion decor market | publisher = ''[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]]'' | date = 28 March 1995| page=L3}}</ref><ref name="The Business Times Mar 1995">{{cite news | author = | title = Pidemco sees $3m rent from Stamford House | publisher = ''[[Business_Times_(Singapore)|The Business Times]]'' | date = 29 March 1995| page=2}}</ref><ref name="Chen Jingwen">{{cite news | author = Chen Jingwen| title = Beyond Orchard Road | publisher = ''[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]]'' | date = 14 July 1995| page=S7}}</ref>

